stateDiagram-v2
    direction TB
    SILENCED --> TRIGGERED: Intervention
    TRIGGERED --> DEMETHYLATING: TET2
    DEMETHYLATING --> POISED: Meth < 0.15
    POISED --> ACTIVE: Meth < 0.02 OR Chromatin > 0.12
    ACTIVE --> hTERTHigh: Expression ↑
    ACTIVE --> REMETHYLATING: Meth rises
    REMETHYLATING --> SILENCED
    hTERTHigh --> TelomereMaintenance
    TelomereMaintenance --> ATM_Sensing: Shelterin feedback
    ATM_Sensing --> DEMETHYLATING
